 Hotel Booking Cancellation System

This project is a **Hotel Booking Cancellation System** that allows users to manage and cancel hotel reservations efficiently. It demonstrates basic functionalities of booking management, including searching, viewing, and canceling reservations.

## Features

- Search for hotel bookings by reservation ID or user details.
- View booking details including dates, room type, and payment status.
- Cancel bookings with confirmation and automatic update of booking status.
- Error handling for invalid reservation IDs or already canceled bookings.
